    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\nT(x) &= (30 + x)(2000 - 5x) + 50x \\\\\n&= -5x^2 + 1900x + 60000, x \\in (0; 400].\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
